      "body" : "To compare \"tonal vs decimal\" to \"english vs all other languages\" is I suspect a vacuous truth. Of course other languages need to be supported - they are already in use. Bitcoin is worthwhile despite USD and Euro existing as it provides needed advantages. What advantages does this change provide? It's a simple question. Can you give a simple answer? Preferably a shorter answer than a book written centuries ago which no one has heard of.",
