      "body" : "Tonal and Dozenal are also already in use. Bitcoin is worthwhile to me *because* of its fitness for a tonal adaptation. The simple key advantage to Tonal over Decimal, is that Tonal is easier for humans to work with, since it is based on just 2s rather than 2 and 5 (which is unnatural to the human mind).",
